name: High Maintenance
description: High Maintenance is a TV series starring Ben Sinclair, Kate Lyn Sheil, and Britt Lower. A comedy that explores the private lives of unique New York individuals through a common thread: their weed deliveryman.

review.name: A very worthy show.
review.reviewBody: It is pure creativity each week and has fascinating stories that share a part of New York few of us would ever see. I recommend it to all of my friends and once they come in touch with the non linear format they too embrace it. Great job everyone involved in this delightful and touching show.

trailer.name: Season 3 Trailer
trailer.description: This season, "High Maintenance" profiles everyday people whose stories of success, failure, love and loss intersect across New York, while delving deeper into personal life of The Guy, who is spending less time on his iconic bicycle and more time in "Steve RV," a set of wheels gifted to him last season.
